, 
<figureCitation box="[271,300,1215,1239]" captionStart="FIGURES 46 – 55" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1704,1726]" captionTargetBox="[152,1434,193,1682]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[152,1434,193,1683]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 46 – 55. Male genitalia of species of Argyrogrammana collected at the PNSD. 46. A. alstonii. 47. A. nurtia ludibunda. 48. A. pulchra. 49. A. bonita. 50. A. amalfreda. 51. A. physis phyton. 52. A. halli sp. nov. paratype. 53. A. celata. 54. A. gallardi sp. nov. paratype from PNSD. 55. A. aparamilla. Left to right: dorsal view of uncus, lateral view of tegumen, saccus, uncus, gnathos, valva and aedeagus, and ventral view of valva. Scale bar = 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233292/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="231">48</figureCitation>
